## Limitations

The information gathered is based on available online resources and may not cover all possible government actions or the latest developments in climate policy. Additionally, the effectiveness of these strategies can vary significantly depending on regional and national contexts, political will, and economic conditions. Further research and expert consultation would be beneficial to gain a comprehensive understanding of the most effective government actions against climate change.